personas.description: Anyone represents a standard user of the app without a specific role. This user has access to functionality that is not explicitly restricted.

Jane is responsible for everything HR related. She hires and fires employees.

Role: HR

Alex is responsible for client acquisition and setting up projects. He keeps track of the time spent on a project.

Role: PM

Maxi represents a developer of the team. She works on different projects and tracks her time.

Role: Dev
